{"tid":992850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府料將放寬申領4,000元手續安排　學生主婦註明身份可免住址證明","createTime":"2019-01-23T13:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T13:14:34.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab17423d2ba2eef8b78a6b7e70fe18565ccf8161","tid":992850,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sy5TnB9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSy5TnB9.png&h=af0d9c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「關愛共享計劃」前日開始派發申請表格，然而被批評安排混亂兼手續繁複。財經事務及庫務局局長劉怡翔今日和政黨會面後，或將放寬手續上的要求，如接受郵費不足的申請表格，及寬鬆處理未能提供住址證明的人士等，詳情將會在明日公布。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆引述當局指，明白現時做法對市民造成困擾，會放寬安排，公屋租約和劏房租約都可以用作住址證明。民建聯立會議員柯創盛指，沒有銀行戶口的人士可以註明自己的情況，當局會安排作現金和支票交收，亦會考慮增加收表地點。<br />\n<br />\n同是立會議員的黨友梁志祥則稱，當局表示露宿者、學生和家庭主婦只需註明其身份，即使沒住址證明，局方也會處理其申請。郵費不足的申請表也可寬鬆處理，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使沒貼郵票的申請表亦有機會獲處理</span>。他批評政府後知後覺，讓人失望。民主黨胡志偉亦透露，當局稱只要將申請表寄到負責執行的「在職家庭及學生資助事務處」，當局均會處理。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔使貼郵票嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"6c4dc3de81154b0d4c81891269f2716db6ec55f3","tid":992850,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/268097/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%984000%E5%85%83%E6%89%8B%E7%BA%8C%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%80%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%BB%E5%A9%A6%E8%A8%BB%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F268097%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E7%2594%25B3%25E9%25A0%25984000%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%258E%2592%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E8%25A8%25BB%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%2F&d=Mxbo3%2FVMs1bg%2BUg7vhJb826kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7feee38c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/268097/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%984000%E5%85%83%E6%89%8B%E7%BA%8C%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%80%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%BB%E5%A9%A6%E8%A8%BB%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB/</a>"},{"pid":"3b956798baad9425601ee59ca78e623d573cfeff","tid":992850,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"$0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}